tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_algorithm_revisions (
    revision_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_name VARCHAR(255),
    author_name VARCHAR(255),
    impact_on_calculations VARCHAR(1024),
    revision_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_algorithm_revisions (
    revision_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_name VARCHAR(255),
    author_name VARCHAR(255),
    revision_date DATE,
    impact_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE algorithm_calculations (
    calculation_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    revision_id INT REFERENCES quantum_algorithm_revisions(revision_id),
    calculation_name VARCHAR(255),
    input_data JSON,
    output_data JSON,
    calculation_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE calculation_history (
    history_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    calculation_id INT REFERENCES algorithm_calculations(calculation_id),
    revision_id INT REFERENCES quantum_algorithm_revisions(revision_id),
    history_date DATE,
    history_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_algorithm_revisions (
    revision_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_name TEXT,
    author_name TEXT,
    revision_date TIMESTAMP,
    impact_on_calculations TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE algorithm_parameters (
    parameter_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    revision_id INT,
    parameter_name TEXT,
    parameter_value TEXT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_revision_id FOREIGN KEY (revision_id) REFERENCES quantum_algorithm_revisions(revision_id)
);

CREATE TABLE algorithm_stats (
    stats_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    revision_id INT,
    execution_time INT,
    memory_usage INT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_revision_id FOREIGN KEY (revision_id) REFERENCES quantum_algorithm_revisions(revision_id)
);

CREATE TABLE algorithm_contributors (
    contributor_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    revision_id INT,
    contributor_name TEXT,
    contributor_email TEXT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_revision_id FOREIGN KEY (revision_id) REFERENCES quantum_algorithm_revisions(revision_id)
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_algorithm_revisions (
    revision_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_name VARCHAR(255),
    author_name VARCHAR(255),
    revision_date DATE,
    impact_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE revision_comments (
    comment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_revision_id INT,
    comment_text TEXT,
    commented_by VARCHAR(255),
    comment_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE calculation_history (
    history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    calculation_id INT,
    calculation_date DATE,
    calculation_author VARCHAR(255),
    revision_impact_description TEXT
);
